com.smjourney.entity

Class EntityPartition

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.smjourney.entity.EntityPartition

  • public class EntityPartition
extends java.lang.Object
    A part of a whole Entity. This entity partition contains the data for which whole Entity it refers to and the individual cell that the entity partition is situated on.
